qryXMLSLATIDetail.Description:
Loose or Smokeless tobacco: 10% of the wholesale cost price;
Little cigars (weighing not more than 3 lbs./thousand): 5 cents/20 cigars;
All other cigars: 23% of the wholesale cost price.

Tobacco dealers/retailers: $10 annually;
Manufacturer, importer and distributor licenses: initial $250 annual fee per place of business, annual renewal fee of $10; 
Cigarette and other tobacco product vending machine licenses: $10 per machine annually.
